WEBVTT

00:00:15.367 --> 00:00:16.993
Deep in the jungles of Vietnam,

00:00:16.993 --> 00:00:18.555
soldiers from both sides

00:00:18.555 --> 00:00:20.229
battled heat exhaustion and each other

00:00:20.229 --> 00:00:22.098
for nearly 20 long years.

00:00:22.098 --> 00:00:23.533
But the key to Communist victory

00:00:23.533 --> 00:00:25.051
wasn't weapons or stamina,

00:00:25.051 --> 00:00:26.881
it was a dirt road.

00:00:26.881 --> 00:00:28.312
The Ho Chi Minh Trail,

00:00:28.312 --> 00:00:30.831
winding through Vietnam, Laos, and Cambodia,